<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Sona Odyssey – Layout Practice</title>
  <style>
    /* --- Base layout --- */
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      color: #111827;
      background: #f9fafb;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .page {
      max-width: 1120px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 40px 20px 80px;
    }

    section {
      margin-bottom: 80px;
    }

    h1, h2, h3 {
      margin: 0 0 16px;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    p {
      margin: 0 0 12px;
    }

    /* --- Reusable spacing helpers --- */
    .stack-8 > * + * { margin-top: 8px; }
    .stack-12 > * + * { margin-top: 12px; }
    .stack-16 > * + * { margin-top: 16px; }
    .stack-24 > * + * { margin-top: 24px; }
    .stack-32 > * + * { margin-top: 32px; }

    /* --- Buttons --- */
    .button-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: background 0.15s ease, color 0.15s ease, border-color 0.15s ease,
                  transform 0.1s ease, box-shadow 0.1s ease;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: #111827;
      color: #f9fafb;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.25);
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      background: #020617;
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.35);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      background: #ffffff;
      color: #111827;
      border-color: #d1d5db;
    }

    .btn-secondary:hover {
      background: #f3f4f6;
      border-color: #9ca3af;
    }

    /* --- HERO --- */
    .hero {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.4fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: 40px;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 40px 0 20px;
    }

    .hero-title {
      font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 4vw, 3.2rem);
      letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    }

    .hero-subtitle {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #4b5563;
      max-width: 28rem;
    }

    .hero-right {
      justify-self: end;
      max-width: 320px;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: #6b7280;
    }

    /* --- MY WORK (portfolio grid) --- */
    .section-heading {
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #111827;
    }

    .divider {
      width: 48px;
      height: 2px;
      background: #111827;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .work-grid {
      margin-top: 24px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .work-card {
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .work-card-title {
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .work-card-meta {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      color: #9ca3af;
    }

    .work-card-desc {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #4b5563;
    }

    /* --- PROFESSIONAL SKILLS (two-column list) --- */
    .skills {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.1fr) minmax(0, 1.2fr);
      gap: 40px;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .skills-intro {
      font-size: 0.98rem;
      color: #4b5563;
      max-width: 22rem;
    }

    .skills-list {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
      gap: 24px 32px;
    }

    .skill-item {
      position: relative;
      padding-left: 16px;
    }

    .skill-item::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      top: 0.4em;
      width: 8px;
      height: 2px;
      background: #111827;
      border-radius: 999px;
    }

    .skill-title {
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .skill-text {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #4b5563;
    }

    /* --- TRAVEL STORIES (blog list style) --- */
    .travel-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: baseline;
      gap: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .travel-subtitle {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: #6b7280;
      max-width: 22rem;
    }

    .travel-list {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.4fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: 32px;
    }

    .travel-posts {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .travel-post {
      padding-bottom: 16px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }

    .travel-post-title {
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .travel-post-meta {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      color: #9ca3af;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .travel-post-excerpt {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #4b5563;
    }

    .travel-aside {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #6b7280;
    }

    /* --- SMALL STRIP --- */
    .strip {
      background: #111827;
      color: #f9fafb;
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 14px 24px;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    /* --- Responsive tweaks --- */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .hero {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }

      .hero-right {
        justify-self: start;
      }

      .skills {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }

      .travel-list {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="page">

    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="stack-24">
        <div class="stack-12">
          <h1 class="hero-title">Sona Odyssey</h1>
          <p class="hero-subtitle">
            The intersection of career and discovery.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="button-row">
          <a href="#my-work" class="btn btn-primary">View Portfolio</a>
          <a href="#travel-stories" class="btn btn-secondary">Explore Travel</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-right stack-16">
        <p>
          A living portfolio of projects, skills, and journeys that go beyond a
          traditional résumé.
        </p>
        <p>
          Use this layout to study how spacing, grids, and buttons work together.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- MY WORK -->
    <section id="my-work">
      <div class="divider"></div>
      <h2 class="section-heading">Selected Projects</h2>

      <div class="work-grid">
        <article class="work-card">
          <div class="work-card-meta">Brand Strategy · 2025</div>
          <div class="work-card-title">Global Repositioning for Tech Brand</div>
          <p class="work-card-desc">
            Led a cross‑market repositioning to align product, story, and visual
            identity across three regions.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="work-card">
          <div class="work-card-meta">Content Systems</div>
          <div class="work-card-title">Knowledge Hub for Remote Teams</div>
          <p class="work-card-desc">
            Built a content framework that turned scattered docs into a single,
            searchable source of truth.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="work-card">
          <div class="work-card-meta">Experience Design</div>
          <div class="work-card-title">Onboarding Journey Redesign</div>
          <p class="work-card-desc">
            Simplified a complex onboarding flow, improving activation and
            reducing drop‑off.
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- PROFESSIONAL SKILLS -->
    <section>
      <h2 class="section-heading">Professional Skills</h2>

      <div class="skills stack-24">
        <p class="skills-intro">
          A blend of strategic leadership, storytelling, and structured
          execution — shaped by both boardrooms and border crossings.
        </p>

        <div class="skills-list">
          <div class="skill-item">
            <div class="skill-title">Strategic Leadership</div>
            <p class="skill-text">
              Guiding complex organizational transitions with a clear narrative
              and measurable outcomes.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="skill-item">
            <div class="skill-title">Global Branding</div>
            <p class="skill-text">
              Developing brand identities that resonate across cultures without
              losing their core.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="skill-item">
            <div class="skill-title">Content Strategy</div>
            <p class="skill-text">
              Turning scattered ideas into structured systems that scale across
              channels and teams.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="skill-item">
            <div class="skill-title">Market Analysis</div>
            <p class="skill-text">
              Using data and field insight to spot patterns, risks, and
              opportunities early.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="skill-item">
            <div class="skill-title">Project Management</div>
            <p class="skill-text">
              Managing complex portfolios with clear scope, timelines, and
              communication.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="skill-item">
            <div class="skill-title">Global Discovery</div>
            <p class="skill-text">
              Bringing lessons from travel and cross‑cultural work back into
              strategy and execution.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- TRAVEL STORIES -->
    <section id="travel-stories">
      <div class="travel-header">
        <div>
          <h2 class="section-heading">Travel Stories</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="travel-subtitle">
          Field notes from journeys that shaped how I think about work, culture,
          and long‑term growth.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="travel-list">
        <div class="travel-posts">
          <article class="travel-post">
            <div class="travel-post-meta">JAPAN · REFLECTION</div>
            <div class="travel-post-title">Learning to Move Slower in Tokyo</div>
            <p class="travel-post-excerpt">
              In a city that never stops, I found the value of deliberate pauses
              — and how they changed my work rhythm.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="travel-post">
            <div class="travel-post-meta">PORTUGAL · CAREER BREAK</div>
            <div class="travel-post-title">Designing a Life, Not a Resume</div>
            <p class="travel-post-excerpt">
              A month on the coast reframed how I think about ambition, rest,
              and long‑term planning.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="travel-post">
            <div class="travel-post-meta">MEXICO CITY · CURIOSITY</div>
            <div class="travel-post-title">Following Questions, Not Itineraries</div>
            <p class="travel-post-excerpt">
              Letting curiosity lead the way opened up new ways of listening —
              to people, places, and projects.
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>

        <aside class="travel-aside stack-16">
          <p>
            Think of this as the “travel blog” side of Sona Odyssey — where
            personal journeys and professional growth overlap.
          </p>
          <p>
            Layout‑wise, this uses a two‑column grid: posts on the left, context
            on the right.
          </p>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SMALL STRIP -->
    <section>
      <div class="strip">
        Professional growth meets global discovery.
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</body>
</html>
